      "id": "PopularPost56928",
      "post_content": "Cool, [Ball Lightning](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ball Lightning) at half power and a third the cost. Or maybe you see it as [Hellspark Elemental](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hellspark Elemental) for half the cost, or half the power for a fourth the cost. Then there are the people who see it as [Lightning Bolt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt), but I think they forget that with this card your opponents choose where the damage goes, not you. Regardless, this cards sits nicely in burn decks that want to win quickly.",
      "posted_by": "Eved",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost56928\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">Cool, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ball Lightning\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ball Lightning\">Ball Lightning</a> at half power and a third the cost. Or maybe you see it as <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hellspark Elemental\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hellspark Elemental\">Hellspark Elemental</a> for half the cost, or half the power for a fourth the cost. Then there are the people who see it as <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lightning Bolt\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt\">Lightning Bolt</a>, but I think they forget that with this card your opponents choose where the damage goes, not you. Regardless, this cards sits nicely in burn decks that want to win quickly.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '56928'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy21588\">Eved</span>\r\n                                (2/28/2010 6:53:03 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starR