    {
      "id": "PopularPost116196",
      "post_content": "i like it over lighting bolt in early game mostly because if they block, they take damage *and* lose a creature. Lighting bolt, while it allows you to chose, dose not have trample or a trample like efect, thus if you decide to destroy a creature with 1 or 2 toughness no damage caries over.",
      "posted_by": "bijart_dauth",
